title: 08/05/21 DPS Hour 2 Babe Laufenberg

description:
Cowboys radio color analyst Babe Laufenberg joins Dan to explain why he thinks the Steelers are more likely to miss the playoffs than the Cowboys, due to a tougher schedule and the Cowboy's weaker division!
